e additional LBVs.\nAG~Car and Hen~3-519 hint that this new information may alter our traditional\nview of LBVs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 17:58:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2017 15:30:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
